des:
You can now listen to Tripotay Lakay on your Alexa-enabled smart devices.

Tripotay Lakay is one of the largest Haitian, News Broadcasting networks on facebook, youtube and other platforms, since October 2015. Staffed 24 hours, seven days a week by a dedicated team around the world to deliver what is happening in Haiti. We stand for excellence in our journalism. We are committed to serving you.

Note: Broadcasting in multilanguages.
